## Code Preview
'''js
const commentSchema = new Schema({
  content: {
    type: String,
    required: true
  },
  user: {
    type: Schema.Types.ObjectId,
    ref: 'User',
    required: true
  },
  userName: {
    type: String,
    required: true
  },
  userAvatar: {
    type: String,
    required: true
  }
}, {
  timestamps: true
});
'''

